commentText: Extract the URL filename from the given request URI._@param uri the request URI_ for example "/index.html"_@return the extracted URI filename_ for example "index"
codeText: protected String extractViewNameFromUrlPath(String uri) {_		int start = (uri.charAt(0) == '/' ? 1 : 0)__		int lastIndex = uri.lastIndexOf(".")__		int end = (lastIndex < 0 ? uri.length() : lastIndex)__		return uri.substring(start, end)__	}
